topics.body:
*WOOHOO!*
So I was checking my email and another person in my programming team got tired of the other guy's shit and finished it for him.

No offense to anyone, but this is one of the reasons why I don't like most people born with a silver spoon born up their ass cause they don't know how to fucking pull their weight, they expect other people to everything for them and then whenever someone thinks they're being fucking lazy they make shit up to justify their reliance on others to do their work for them.

Two of the guys in our group did their fair share but nothing more, can't fault them for that, but the guy I'm getting pissed off about wouldn't pull his fucking weight and we were *TWO MONTHS LATE* with the project cause he wouldn't fucking do his work and he expected us to do it for him.  The final guy in the group is a fucking god send cause I didn't know the first clue about how the lazy guy's programming chunk worked cause it was complete ass that didn't make sense, but the final guy in the group got tired of the lazy guy's shit and finished it for him even though he had a job, a family and such whereas the lazy fucker doesn't have to and just sits at his parent's house and such.



On a side note: today I learned how come there's so many stupid fuckers high up in the world; they act helpless and force people working with them to do their work and then take credit for everything in the end.


I am so fucking glad to be done with this cause legit how the fuck does that lazy guy even function; does his parents still have to spoon feed him and wipe his ass or something cause christ does he act helpless.

I'm pissed off at that fucker, but I'm also relieved that everyone just got tired of his shit.
